OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1773191771
OL,3,CHealth and education systems
OL,4,C'underperforming' says think tank
OL,6,FWales' health and education systems
OL,7,Fare 'underperforming' compared to
OL,8,Fthose in England despite significant
OL,9,Fincreases in spending, according to
OL,10,Fnew research .
OL,12,FThe report by the Institute for Fiscal
OL,13,FStudies (IFS) found that performance
OL,14,Facross both sectors in Wales is now
OL,15,Fsubstantially worse than before the
OL,16,FCOVID-19 pandemic and weaker than in
OL,17,FEngland on a range of key measures.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
