OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1773191771
OL,3,CHealth and education systems
OL,4,C'underperforming' says think tank
OL,6,FHowever, in response, Laura Doel,
OL,7,Fnational secretary at NAHT Cymru,
OL,8,Fsaid: "School leaders in Wales are
OL,9,Fworking hard to deliver for their
OL,10,Fpupils amid all manner of challenges `
OL,11,Ffrom funding shortfalls and supporting
OL,12,Fchildren with additional learning
OL,13,Fneeds (ALN), to issues outside school
OL,14,Fwhich can affect attendance and
OL,15,Fattainment.
OL,26,@pD@GOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
