CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1773191771
OL,3,CHealth and education systems
OL,4,C'underperforming' says think tank
OL,6,F"While the PISA analysis can be
OL,7,Fuseful, we should not over-interpret
OL,8,Fthese results and rely on simplistic
OL,9,Fcomparisons which may not capture the
OL,10,Frichness of children's learning or the
OL,11,Fdifferent stages of education policy
OL,12,Fdevelopment in different countries."
OL,14,FThe report found that pupils in the
OL,15,Fmiddle of the income distribution in
OL,16,FWales perform, on average, at a
OL,17,Fsimilar level to the poorest fifth of
OL,18,Fpupils in England.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
