CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1773191771
OL,3,CHealth and education systems
OL,4,C'underperforming' says think tank
OL,6,FDespite these outcomes, spending on
OL,7,Fboth health and education has risen
OL,8,Fsignificantly in recent years. Health
OL,9,Fspending per person in Wales has
OL,10,Fincreased by 17% in real terms since
OL,11,F2019`20, while spending per pupil has
OL,12,Fgrown by 14% over the same period.
OL,14,FOverall spending per person on health
OL,15,Fand schools combined is higher in
OL,16,FWales than in every English region
OL,17,Fexcept Greater London. Researchers
OL,18,Fadded that funding levels alone do not
OL,19,Fappear to explain the weaker
OL,20,Fperformance.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1773191771
OL,3,CHealth and education systems
OL,4,C'underperforming' says think tank
OL,6,FResponding to the findings, the Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment said they're continuing to
OL,8,F"work closely with health boards and
OL,9,Flocal authorities to improve frontline
OL,10,Fpublic services at a time when costs
OL,11,Fare rising."
OL,13,FThey also added: "The NHS waiting list
OL,14,Fhas fallen and the longest waits are
OL,15,Fcoming down. We have set clear
OL,16,Fexpectations for all health boards to
OL,17,Freduce emergency department long stays
OL,18,Fand complete ambulance handovers
OL,19,Fwithin 45 minutes.
OL,26,@uD@ROU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
