OL,3,CHealth and education systems
OL,4,C'underperforming' says think tank
OL,6,F"Our education system is moving in the
OL,7,Fright direction thanks to the
OL,8,Fadditional support we are providing to
OL,9,Fschools and the hard work of school
OL,10,Fstaff. Our latest GCSE and A level
OL,11,Fresults show improvements in
OL,12,Fattainment since 2024. For younger
OL,13,Flearners we are seeing progress within
OL,14,Freading and numeracy in personalised
OL,15,Fassessments."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@MO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
