OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1773191771
OL,3,CHealth and education systems
OL,4,C'underperforming' says think tank
OL,6,FHowever, Welsh Conservative Shadow
OL,7,FCabinet Secretary for Health and
OL,8,FSocial Care, Peter Fox MS said:
OL,9,F"Today's report from the Institute for
OL,10,FFiscal Studies confirms that after 27
OL,11,Fyears, decisions made by Labour and
OL,12,FPlaid Cymru have left our public
OL,13,Fservices in a mess.
OL,15,F"Despite spending on health increasing
OL,16,Fsignificantly, patients are waiting
OL,17,Flonger for treatment and A&E
OL,18,Fperformance continues to worsen.
OL,26,@qD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
