OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1773191771
OL,3,CHealth and education systems
OL,4,C'underperforming' says think tank
OL,6,F"The Welsh Conservatives have a clear
OL,7,Fand credible plan to cut wasteful
OL,8,Fspending, restore performance, cut
OL,9,Fwaiting times and deliver the timely
OL,10,Fcare people across Wales deserve."
OL,12,FPlaid Cymru health spokesperson, Mabon
OL,13,Fap Gwynfor MS, said: "This report
OL,14,Fconfirms what people across Wales
OL,15,Falready know ` the state of our NHS
OL,16,Fand our schools is simply not good
OL,17,Fenough. After 27 years in power, this
OL,18,Fdecline is the direct result of
OL,19,FLabour's mismanagement, and people
OL,20,Fhave every right to be angry about it."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@bO]uD@VOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/13
